Package concurrent_multiset

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConcurrentMultiset<T>
    The interface that defines the methods that each implementation of a concurrent multiset must provide.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FineGrainMultiset<T>
    The fine grain implementation of a concurrent multiset.
    FineGrainMultiset.MultisetElement<T>
    The class that defines the entry of a fine grain multiset.
    LazyMultiset<T>
    The lazy implementation of a concurrent multiset.
    LazyMultiset.MultisetElement<T>
    The class that defines the entry of a lazy multiset.
    LockFreeMultiset<T>
    The lock free implementation of a concurrent multiset.
    LockFreeMultiset.MultisetElement<T>
    The class that defines the entry of a lock free multiset.
    MultisetLock
    The definition of a lock utilized to block the ConcurrentMultiset.add(Object, int) and ConcurrentMultiset.remove(Object, int) operations while someone is executing a ConcurrentMultiset.removeAll(Collection) on the multiset.
